<plot>Tom's sweetheart is Vicky, the sister of the town sheriff. One day when Tom comes to town, he heads to a saloon and starts to drink. By the time that his friend Ned arrives, Tom has had a lot to drink, and when a scuffle breaks out soon afterwards, Tom shoots Ned in the confusion. Thinking that he has killed Ned, Tom leaves town for good. The sheriff, though, is still interested in bringing Tom in if he gets the chance.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?393635</url></doc>
